  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0bae\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Introducing Premium for high-end air travelers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bandaranaike International Airport (BIA) yesterday inaugurated the 'Golden Route' arrivals lounge to provide a premium airport experience to high-class passengers traveling through the airport.",
        "The new route was inaugurated by Ports, Shipping and Aviation Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva, who said the new service would contribute to earning additional foreign currency for the country.",
        "International airports offer exclusive passenger services for their premium passengers. Especially for high net worth individuals (HNWIs) who expect premium services at airports, he said.",
        "Air travelers with higher incomes can access this lane without queuing for airport formalities such as immigration and immigration procedures, customs checks, food and communication requirements.",
        "At present, BIA only provides Silk Road service facility for commercially important passengers. It is not aimed at HNWIs.",
        "At the Cold Route Lounge, guests can enjoy an expedited check-in process including customs, immigration and immigration and all other formalities.",
        "The new service facility will be offered to passengers for a fee of US$200 (per arrival or departure) and can be booked through www.airport.lk."
      ],
